      <title>南非政府将公务员薪酬提高至 4.7%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/south-african-government-raises-civil-servant-pay-offer-to-4-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非政府将该国公务员的工资涨幅提高至 4.7%，远低于代表 130 万公务员的工会提出的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/south-african-government-raises-civil-servant-pay-offer-to-4-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 17:20:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
