      <title>贝索斯称该帖未予认可是为了避免媒体偏见</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/jeff-bezos-explains-post-s-decision-not-to-endorse-a-candidate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司创始人、华盛顿邮报老板杰夫·贝佐斯表示，该报停止支持总统候选人的决定解决了困扰媒体行业的“信誉危机”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/jeff-bezos-explains-post-s-decision-not-to-endorse-a-candidate</guid>
